OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FThe Snowman illustrator    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FRaymond Briggs dies at 88  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Author-illustrator Raymond Briggs,     
OL,6, best-known for his 1978 classic The    
OL,7, Snowman, has died at the age of 88.    
OL,9,FHis death was confirmed by his family, 
OL,10,Fwho said he "was much loved and will be
OL,11,Fdeeply missed".                        
OL,13,F"We know that Raymond's books were     
OL,14,Floved by and touched millions of people
OL,15,Faround the world, who will be sad to   
OL,16,Fhear this news," they said, in a       
OL,17,Fstatement on Wednesday.                
OL,19,FThe Snowman was turned into a Bafta TV 
OL,20,Faward-winning animated TV film in 1982.
